  "description": "3 Schritte zum Erfolg - Timeline-Style",
  "template": "<section class=\"{{spacing}} bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white\">\n  <div class=\"{{containerWidth}} mx-auto px-6\">\n    <div class=\"text-center mb-16\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl {{fontFamily}} {{fontWeight}} mb-4 text-[{{textColor}}]\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n        In 3 Schritten zu deinem ersten Training\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"text-lg text-[{{textColor}}]/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto {{fontSize}}\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n        So einfach startest du bei uns durch\n      </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative\">\n      <!-- Verbindungslinien -->\n      <div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-20 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[{{primaryColor}}] via-[{{accentColor}}] to-[{{primaryColor}}] opacity-20\"></div>\n      \n      <div class=\"relative text-center group\">\n        <div class=\"relative inline-block mb-6\">\n          <div class=\"w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[{{primaryColor}}] to-[{{accentColor}}] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl {{fontWeight}} shadow-xl group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-300\">\n            1\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-[{{accentColor}}] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-check text-white text-sm\"></i>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"text-2xl {{fontWeight}} mb-3 text-[{{textColor}}]\" contenteditable=\"true\">Anmelden</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-[{{textColor}}]/70 {{fontSize}} leading-relaxed\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n          Schließe online deinen Vertrag ab oder komm direkt ins Studio. Personalausweis nicht vergessen!\n        </p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"relative text-center group\">\n        <div class=\"relative inline-block mb-6\">\n          <div class=\"w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[{{primaryColor}}] to-[{{accentColor}}] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl {{fontWeight}} shadow-xl group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-300\">\n            2\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-[{{accentColor}}] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-check text-white text-sm\"></i>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"text-2xl {{fontWeight}} mb-3 text-[{{textColor}}]\" contenteditable=\"true\">Chip abholen</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-[{{textColor}}]/70 {{fontSize}} leading-relaxed\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n          Bei deinem ersten Besuch bekommst du deinen persönlichen Chip für 24/7 Zugang zum Studio.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"relative text-center group\">\n        <div class=\"relative inline-block mb-6\">\n          <div class=\"w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[{{primaryColor}}] to-[{{accentColor}}] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl {{fontWeight}} shadow-xl group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-300\">\n            3\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-[{{accentColor}}] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-fire text-white text-sm\"></i>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"text-2xl {{fontWeight}} mb-3 text-[{{textColor}}]\" contenteditable=\"true\">Durchstarten</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-[{{textColor}}]/70 {{fontSize}} leading-relaxed\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n          Bring deine Sportkleidung mit und leg direkt los. Viel Spaß beim ersten Training!\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"
}
